{"type":"message","id":"8469ee16","parentId":"ebf12bc3","timestamp":"2026-02-27T04:01:47.500Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent\n\nExecuting coordinator heartbeat health checks at 12:00...\n\n### System Health Check\n- ✅ All agents active (Main, Stock, MCS)\n- ✅ Communication protocol operational  \n- ✅ Memory system accessible\n- ✅ No critical issues detected\n\n### Agent Coordination Status\n- **Stock Agent**: Health check ping sent - status confirmed\n- **MCS Agent**: Health check ping sent - status confirmed\n- **Main Agent**: System coordination functioning normally\n\nAll systems are running smoothly. Heartbeat completed successfully at 12:00."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":63449,"output":121,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772164896068}}
