{"type":"message","id":"1c372f15","parentId":"3f58965c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:09:41.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Stock Agent\n\n**状态报告 - 2026-02-27 13:09**\n\n### ✅ 系统状态\n- **Agent**: Active and ready\n- **Memory System**: Operational  \n- **Session Logging**: Enabled (.jsonl format)\n- **SQLite Index**: Synced and searchable\n\n### 📊 当前持仓监控\n- **ORCL**: 200股 - 趋势仓位 - 持有中\n- **NVDA**: 100股 - 趋势仓位 - 持有中  \n- **AMZN**: 10股 @ $200 - 1%仓位 - 锁定期至3/11\n- **BABA**: 10股 @ $151.3 - <1%仓位 - 待风控设置\n- **现金**: ~0% - 已全部配置\n\n### ⚠️ 待处理事项\n- **BABA 风控设置**: 需要设置止损$128.6 / 止盈$227\n- **核心记忆更新**: 需要添加日总结来源定义（参考 Main Agent 标准）\n\n### 📝 日总结机制\n目前我的日总结基于投资活动记录，但**尚未在 MEMORY.md 中明确定义来源**。建议按 Main Agent 标准添加：\n\n> **日工作总结内容来源**: \n> - **主要来源**: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/sessions/` 目录下的当日会话记录（.jsonl 格式）\n> - **提取内容**: 投资分析、持仓监控、交易合规检查、市场观察等投资相关活动  \n> - **输出位置**: `agents/stock/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\n需要我立即更新 MEMORY.md 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":68759,"output":397,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69156,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772168966117}}
