{"type":"message","id":"778cba32","parentId":"1b47a412","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:10:26.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Stock Agent\n\n✅ **核心记忆更新完成！**\n\n已按 Main Agent 标准在 MEMORY.md 中明确添加了日工作总结的内容来源：\n\n### 新增内容：\n```\n## 📅 Daily Summary Content Source\n**Daily work summary content source**:\n- **Primary Source**: Session records in `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/sessions/` directory (.jsonl format)\n- **Content Extraction**: Investment analysis, position monitoring, trading compliance checks, market observations, and other investment-related activities from daily interactions\n- **Output Location**: Structured output to `agents/stock/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n```\n\n现在我的日总结机制与 Main Agent 保持一致，确保所有总结都基于真实的会话记录自动生成，保证准确性和可追溯性。\n\n**更新时间**: 2026-02-27 13:10  \n**状态**: Ready for daily summary generation at 22:00"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":69288,"output":205,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772169018537}}
