{"type":"message","id":"d4fe2ebc","parentId":"d3ed7ef2","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:17:40.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent\n\n实际上 **Stock Agent 和 MCS Agent 已经启动并运行了**！让我证明给您看：\n\n### ✅ 确认子agent状态：\n\n**1. Stock Agent - 已激活**\n- **会话ID**: `17716550-be06-4a13-acae-f3051e0fbf6e`\n- **最后活动**: 2026-02-26 22:01 (昨天的22:00备份时间)\n- **会话文件**: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/sessions/17716550-be06-4a13-acae-f3051e0fbf6e.jsonl` (154KB)\n\n**2. MCS Agent - 已激活**  \n- **会话ID**: `f81a4a2f-75d7-481b-9475-179beb7f9ba0`\n- **最后活动**: 2026-02-26 22:05 (昨天的22:05备份时间)\n- **会话文件**: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/mcs/sessions/f81a4a2f-75d7-481b-9475-179beb7f9ba0.jsonl` (124KB)\n\n### 🔄 为什么看起来\"没启动\"？\n- **按需激活**: OpenClaw 的 agents 是**按需激活**的，不是常驻进程\n- **最近活动**: 它们在昨天22:00-22:05的每日备份流程中正常工作\n- **当前状态**: 没有新消息时，它们处于待命状态（这是正常行为）\n\n### 📝 关于核心记忆更新：\n我刚刚已经更新了 **Stock Agent** 的 MEMORY.md。现在让我立即更新 **MCS Agent** 的 MEMORY.md：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8e299b3fa4a74efc8d59f882","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/mcs/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":71911,"output":488,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72399,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772169444142}}
