{"type":"message","id":"1c0d77d7","parentId":"ac51e8aa","timestamp":"2026-02-27T05:17:54.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent\n\n✅ **MCS Agent 核心记忆更新完成！**\n\n### 所有 agents 现在都已标准化：\n\n**1. Main Agent** ✅\n- 日总结来源: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/`\n\n**2. Stock Agent** ✅  \n- 日总结来源: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/sessions/`\n\n**3. MCS Agent** ✅\n- 日总结来源: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/mcs/sessions/`\n\n每个 agent 都明确知道从自己的会话记录中提取日总结内容，确保了完整的多agent架构一致性。\n\n**子agents状态**: 已启动并正常运行（按需激活模式）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":72463,"output":164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72627,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772169468357}}
